{"tid":1941361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《崩堤之夏》當香港反送中運動遇上殺人事件","createTime":"2020-03-24T11:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T11:20:49.000Z","uid":264138,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6689c7d0c50d86040f14ac5c62e2da8cb085427a","tid":1941361,"uid":264138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/atD3u2V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FatD3u2V.jpg&h=3f2231ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《崩堤之夏》用香港作家的視角闡述反送中事件的爭議性與社會觀點，在虛構中描寫真實。藉由虛構的謀殺案件統整出事件脈絡，從不同視角紀念真實。<br />\n<br />\n反送中遊行後的夜晚、公園凌晨三點的吵鬧人聲、廁所外連儂牆滿滿的起底海報一夜消失、一具血跡斑斑的屍體突然出現。三個有極端政治立場暴力傾向的前科嫌疑犯，千絲萬縷匯聚於黃大仙摩士公園殺人案，究竟死者是他殺、自殺、黑警殺人還是隨機殺人？案情逐漸膠著沉滯，催淚煙霧瀰漫全港，城中喧囂紛擾不絕，一步一步將夏天崩堤&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n《#崩堤之夏》⏰ 4/2全面上市，歷史永不遺忘！<br />\n博客來：<a href=\"https://is.gd/58Z0x2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2F58Z0x2&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=8bdb89cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/58Z0x2</a><br />\n金石堂：<a href=\"https://is.gd/hDA8je\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FhDA8je&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=5aa07e2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/hDA8je</a><br />\n誠品：<a href=\"https://is.gd/4Jz5XM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2F4Jz5XM&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=da1b40c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/4Jz5XM</a><br />\n讀書花園：<a href=\"https://is.gd/LbVE1V\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FLbVE1V&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=5b3077c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/LbVE1V</a><br />\n<br />\n評<br />\n一個字: 買<br />\n兩個字: 必買<br />\n三個字: 香港人<br />\n四個字: 缺一不可<br />\n五個字: 我要佢簽名<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/curonecoc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.faceb